               </p>
               <p>Canter <rs id="t17960914-87-punish487" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17960914-87-punish487" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960914-87-punish487" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="newgate"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960914-87-defend849 t17960914-87-punish487"></join>
               imprisoned one year in Newgate
            </rs>, and fined 1s.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice ROOKE.</p>
